"Java three frameworks" - Liu Guoqing
1. MVC framework: struts2, springmvc. mvc ideas, the implementation process, the main concepts of core classes;
2. ORM framework: hibernate. Framework, the concept of core classes;
3. Lightweight ioc framework: spring, guice. Dependency Injection and Inversion of Control concept;
4. Spring core classes introduced wireframes, Guice introduce the concept;
5. Case Studies;

"Big Data era with NOSQL rise" - Island Domingo
1. background: Web2.0 and the rise of mobile Internet, massive waves of incoming data;
2. Opportunities and Challenges: How to save huge amounts of data, the traditional relational database with the emerging non-relational database;
3. non-relational databases: Redis introduction and use;

